#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans immovable: Pond
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1090 input:1090
#: standard
msgid ""
"Ponds with water becomes dry after some time. These dry holes vanish after a "
"while."
msgstr ""
"Polen mit Water worden na eeniger Tied dröge. Deese drögen Locken gahn na "
"eeniger Tied weg."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans immovable: Pond
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1097 input:1097
#: standard
msgid ""
"When gardeners dig up earth, they leave holes with water in the ground. "
"These falls dry after a while or can be used by terraformer to produce new "
"soil."
msgstr ""
"Wenn Gaardners Klei upgraven, blieven Locken mit Water in de Grund torügg. "
"Se worden na eeniger Tied dröge of könen vun eenem Landumackereerer bruukt "
"worden, um neje Eer to maken."

