msgid ""
"This tree is only planted by the amazon tribe but can be harvested for logs."
msgstr ""
"Deeser Boom word blot vun dat amazoonsk Volk plant, kann aver för "
"Boomstammen kappt worden."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans warehouse: Headquarters
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1338 input:1338
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Accommodation for your people. Also stores your wares and tools."
msgstr "Brengt diene Lüü unner un verwahrt diene Waren un anner Kraam."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Europeans warehouse: Headquarters
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1340 input:1340
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "The headquarters is your main building."
msgstr "Dat Raadhuus is dien wichtigstes Huus."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans warehouse: Port
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1347
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1354 input:1347
#: input:1354 standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"Serves as a base for overseas colonization and trade. Also stores your "
"soldiers, wares and tools."
msgstr ""
"Deent tum Begünnen vun Hannel un Söken över Seefahrt. Brengt ok diene Lüü un "
"Soldaten unner un verwahrt diene Waren un anner Kraam."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans market: Market
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1362 input:1362
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "A market enables trading with other tribes."
msgstr "Een Markt lett di mit anner Völkers hanneln."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Water Gatherer's Hut
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1370 input:1370
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Draws water out of the rivers and lakes."
msgstr "Hisst Water ut de Stromen un Meren."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Europeans production site: Water Gatherer's Hut, part 1
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1373 input:1373
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"The water gatherer’s hut needs open water within the work area. Your workers "
"cannot dig up water from the ground!"
msgstr ""
"De Water-Pottjerske-Kaat bruukt open Water in de Arbeidsgewest. Diene "
"Arbeidersken könen ’t nich ut de Eer graven!"

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Europeans production site: Water Gatherer's Hut, part 2
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1375 input:1375
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Roads and trees along the shoreline block drawing water."
msgstr "Straten un Bomen up de Küst hinnern ’t Halen vun Water."

