msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "The lumberjack’s hut needs trees to fell within the work area."
msgstr "De Boomhauerkaat bruukt Bomen tum Umkappen in de Arbeidsgewest."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Europeans production site: Woodcutters House
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1421 input:1421
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "The lumberjack’s house needs trees to fell within the work area."
msgstr "De Boomhauerhuus bruukt Bomen tum Umkappen in de Arbeidsgewest."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Liana Cutter's Hut
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1428 input:1428
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Home of the liana cutter who cuts lianas for making ropes."
msgstr ""
"Hier wohnt de Boomreep-Slagerske, well Boomreep sleit, daarmit daar Tauen ut "
"maakt worden könen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Europeans production site: Liana Cutter's Hut
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1430 input:1430
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"The liana cutter harvests liana from fully matured trees within the work "
"area which are not being used as lookouts."
msgstr ""
"De Boomreep-Slagerske arnt Boomreep vun utwassen Bomen in de Arbeidsgewest, "
"wat nich as Postjes bruukt worden."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Rare Tree Cutter's Hut
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1437 input:1437
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"Harvests rare trees in the surrounding area. Delivers ironwood, balsa and "
"rubber."
msgstr ""
"Arnt Edelholten in de Naberskupp un maakt daarut Iesenholt, Balsa un Gummi "
"elasticum."

