msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "This farm needs free space within the work area to plant seeds."
msgstr ""
"Deese Buurderee bruukt freje Rüümte in de Arbeidsgewest, waar Ackers plant "
"worden könen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for Europeans production site: Vineyard
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1627 input:1627
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Sows and harvests grape."
msgstr "Sait un arnt Wiendruven."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Europeans production site: Berry Farm
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1636 input:1636
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Plants berry bushes in the surrounding area."
msgstr "Plant Busken in de Naberskupp."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Europeans production site: Berry Farm
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1638 input:1638
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"The berry farm needs free space within the work area to plant the bushes."
msgstr ""
"De Buskenplanteree bruukt freje Rüümte in de Arbeidsgewest, waar Busken "
"plant worden könen."

