#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Spider Farm
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1771 input:1771
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Breeds spiders for silk."
msgstr "Tücht Spinnen för hör Siede."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Cattle Farm
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1778 input:1778
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Breeds strong oxen for adding them to the transportation system."
msgstr "Tücht stevige Ossen för dat Stratennett."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Tapir Farm
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1785 input:1785
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Breeds tapirs for adding them to the transportation system."
msgstr "Tücht Tapiren för dat Stratennett."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Horse Farm
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1792 input:1792
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Breeds the strong horses for adding them to the transportation system."
msgstr "Tücht de stevigen Peer för dat Stratennett."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Donkey Farm
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1799 input:1799
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"Breeds cute and helpful donkeys for adding them to the transportation system."
msgstr "Tücht nüte, godige Langohren för dat Stratennett."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Sheep Farm
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1806 input:1806
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Keeps sheep for their wool."
msgstr "Tücht Schapen för hör Wull."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Europeans production site: Reindeer Farm
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1813 input:1813
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"Breeds strong reindeer for adding them to the transportation system. Also "
"keeps them for their fur, which is turned into armor and cloth."
msgstr ""
"Tücht stevige Sneeihirsken för dat Stratennett. Se worden ok för hör Fell "
"tücht, wat man för Kluften un Stoff bruukt."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Europeans production site: Weaving Mill
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1820 input:1820
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Weaves cloth out of reed."
msgstr "Weevt Stoff ut Reit."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Weaving Mill
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1827 input:1827
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Weaves cloth out of cotton and rope out of liana."
msgstr "Weevt Stoff ut Boomwull un Tauen ut Boomreep."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Weaving Mill
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1834 input:1834
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"Weaves cloth out of cotton, spidercloth out of spider silk and rope out of "
"liana."
msgstr ""
"Weevt Stoff ut Boomwull, Spinnenstoff ut Spinnensied un Tauen ut Boomreep."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Weaving Mill
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1841 input:1841
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"Weaves cloth out of wool, spidercloth out of spider silk and rope out of "
"liana."
msgstr "Weevt Stoff ut Wull, Spinnenstoff ut Spinnensied un Tauen ut Boomreep."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Weaving Mill
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1848 input:1848
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"Weaves cloth out of cotton or wool, spidercloth out of spider silk and rope "
"out of liana. Additional creates armor for soliders."
msgstr ""
"Weevt Stoff ut Boomwull of Wull, Spinnenstoff ut Spinnensied un Tauen ut "
"Boomreep. Maakt ok Wapenrocken för Soldaten."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Europeans production site: Diker's House
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1855 input:1855
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Constructs breakwaters nearby to gain new land from the sea."
msgstr "Baut Lahnungen in de Naberskupp, um Land vun de See to winnen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Europeans production site: Diker's House
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1857 input:1857
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"The diker will terraform the land around each breakwater he builds several "
"times. You can manually remove breakwaters when the land is sufficiently "
"secured to prevent wasting resources; to do so, build a flag, road, or "
"building in the dike’s place."
msgstr ""
"De Diekbauer wannelt dat Land um elkeen Lahnung, wat he baut, mennigmaal um. "
"Du kannst de Lahnung vun Hand wegmaken, wenn dat Land seker genoog is, "
"daarmit keene Mineraale verklüngelt worden; bau daarto eene Fahn of Straat "
"of een Huus in hör Stee."

