#: input:2111 input:2129 input:2138 input:2147 input:2156 input:2165 input:2174
#: input:2183 input:2192 input:2201 standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"If you’re low on soldiers to occupy new military sites, use the downward "
"arrow button to decrease the capacity. You can also click on a soldier to "
"send him away."
msgstr ""
"Wenn du nich genoog Soldaten hest, um neje Soldateree-Boen to besetten, "
"kannst du de Tahl vun Soldaten mit de Piel-runner-Knoop minnern. Du kannst "
"ok eenen Soldat anklicken, um hüm wegtostüren."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Europeans military site: Blockhouse
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:2120 input:2120
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Modified version which can placed on mountains."
msgstr "Ännert Versioon, wat up Bargen baut worden kann."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for an Europeans building: Construction Site
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:2209 input:2209
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "‘Don’t swear at the builder who is short of building materials.’"
msgstr "»Schimp nich tegen de Baukeerl, well keen Baukraam hett.«"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for an Europeans building: Construction Site
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:2211 input:2211
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Proverb widely used for impossible tasks of any kind"
msgstr "Seggwies, wat över all Aarden vun unmögelken Upgaven seggt word"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans building: Construction Site
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:2213 input:2213
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "A new building is being built at this construction site."
msgstr "An deeser Baustee word een nejes Huus baut."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for an Europeans building: Dismantle Site
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:2220 input:2220
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "‘New paths will appear when you are willing to tear down the old.’"
msgstr "»Neje Padden kummen ut, wenn du de ollen ok mal plattrietst.«"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for an Europeans building: Dismantle Site
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:2222 input:2222
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Proverb"
msgstr "Seggwies"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans building: Dismantle Site
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:2224 input:2224
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"A building is being dismantled at this dismantle site, returning some of the "
"resources that were used during this building’s construction to your tribe’s "
"stores."
msgstr ""
"Hier word een Huus plattreten, um eenige Waren torüggtokriegen, de tum Bauen "
"verwendt wurren."

